      <title>最高法院推翻雪佛龙裁决，打击代理权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-overturns-chevron-ruling-in-blow-to-agency-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院意见分歧，推翻了已有数十年历史的法律原则，该原则授权联邦监管机构解释不明确的法律，并发布了一项重磅裁决，将对环境、消费者和金融监管机构形成约束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/supreme-court-overturns-chevron-ruling-in-blow-to-agency-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 14:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 称立法胜利为货币政策调整铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-says-legislative-win-paves-way-for-monetary-policy-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱周五表示，他的政府将改变货币政策框架，这是他首次取得重大立法胜利，确保了其具有里程碑意义的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/milei-says-legislative-win-paves-way-for-monetary-policy-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
